snippet.textDisplay:
Assalamualaikum Abida Parveen sahiba.
                Mai aap se Milne ki tamanna toh rakhta hoon, magar mukaddar mein yeh hai ya nahi, Mai nahi jaanta.
       Lekin aap hamesha mere Dil mei rahoge.Mai maanta Hoon ke aap mere murshid-e- mohtarma hai.Maula se ishq karna Maine aap se seekha hai.

Maula aap ko hayaatee de aur aap par tamaam salamatein naazil ho.

I must say, I love you aabida ji, I love you forever.
